asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Dr Milton H Fluffinson
description:
Dr Milton H Fluffinson of Phoenix Arizona shuffled off his human form in 1980, spending over 40 years in the middle of nowhere until he found his way to FlufWorld in 2021.

A master of conversational hypnosis, Fluffinson is often referred to as The Miracle Worker or The Wizard of the Desert.

Renowned for his extraordinary hypnotic abilities, Fluffinson has the ability to transform lives in the course of a seemingly ordinary conversation. Clients and students alike report life-altering insights and brain-changing realisations that completely reorder their experience of life (in wonderful directions).

Fascinated by the nature of perception, Fluffinson famously conducted experiments with LSD pioneer and author of Brave New World, Aldous Huxley, hypnotising him to the point where he was floridly hallucinating. 

And while Fluffinson confined his  human explorations to the psychedelic nature of perception itself, he will be opening new doors and exploring new possibilities once he starts working with the wonders of mycelium.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
